data.description: Welcome to 1758 West Avenue H1, nestled in the heart of Lancaster! This exquisite single-family home boasts 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, encompassing 2,640 square feet of living space on a generous 6,771 square foot lot. Upon entry, you'll be captivated by the well-thought-out floor plan, complemented by tile floors and recessed lighting throughout. The spacious living room, adorned with a fireplace, sets the stage for cozy winter nights. The dining area and chef's kitchen, complete with a large island featuring a breakfast nook, modern appliances, and ample storage and counter space, create a perfect space for gatherings. The home features 5 well-sized bedrooms, each equipped with closets, and 3 well-appointed bathrooms. The primary bathroom is a luxurious retreat, offering a soaking tub and standing shower. Convenience is enhanced with a dedicated laundry room. Head outside to the open patio and fenced backyard, providing a private outdoor space to relax and unwind. This beautiful home does come with solar panels that are completely paid off and will save you a lot of money in the summer months. Centrally located in Lancaster, this home enjoys proximity to schools, shopping, dining, and convenient freeway access. For more information, call us today and explore the charm of 1758 West Avenue H1!
